<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>FAQ</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/faq.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #ffe4e1;
            /* Soft pink background */
            color: #333;
            /* Dark grey text */
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .faq-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            /* White background */
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            /* Soft shadow */
        }
        
        .faq-title {
            color: #ff69b4;
            /* Pink title */
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .faq-item {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ffb6c1;
            /* Light pink border */
            padding: 10px 0;
        }
        
        .faq-item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        .faq-question {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #ff69b4;
            /* Pink question */
        }
        
        .faq-answer {
            color: #666;
            /* Medium grey text */
            padding-left: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="faq-container">
        <h1 class="faq-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">What is this website about?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">This website is a blog platform where users can create and share their own blog posts.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">How do I create a blog post?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">To create a blog post, click on the "Create Blog" button on the homepage, fill in the title and content, and submit your post.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">Can I edit my blog post after publishing?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">Yes, you can edit your blog post by clicking on the "Edit" button next to your post in the "Created Blogs" section.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">How do I delete a blog post?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">To delete a blog post, click on the "Delete" button next to your post in the "Created Blogs" section.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">Is there a way to search for blog posts?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">Currently, the search feature is not available, but we are working on adding it in the future.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">Who can see my blog posts?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">All blog posts are public and can be viewed by anyone who visits the website.</div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <%- include('partials/footer.ejs') %>

</body>

</html>